{{etyl|frm}} ''[[rêver#Middle French|rêver]]'' "to wander, be lost in vague thoughts, induce in error" from {{etyl|fro}} ''[[resver#Old French|resver]]'' "to consider, reflect, be delirious", probably of {{etyl|gem}} origin, from {{etyl|frk}} *''[[raswjan#Frankish|rāswan, rēswan]]'' "to consider, conjecture" from {{proto|Germanic|ræsi-, rǣsw-|to think, suppose, consider|lang=}} from {{proto|Indo-European|rei-|to reason, count|lang=}}. Akin to {{etyl|ang|-}} ''[[ræswan#Old English|rǣswan]]'' "to think, consider, suspect, conjecture".

